dcterms:description: The Tencent Transfer Learning (TTL) dataset contains users’ recent 100 interactions on the QQ Browser platform and provides downstream labeled data for user profiling tasks and cold-recommendation tasks.
dcterms:title: Tencent Transfer Learning (TTL) dataset

dcterms:creator: OPPO Research Institute
dcterms:description: The App dataset consists of users’ app installation behaviors collected from a worldwide smartphone manufacturer, OPPO, and provides downstream labeled data for gender prediction and CVR prediction tasks.
dcterms:title: App dataset
